    <p class="eyebrow"><span class="signal"></span>Electric mobility guides</p><h1>Practical information for charging with more confidence.</h1><p>Clear guidance for the questions that come up before a trip, while choosing a charger and when organizing your charging routine.</p>
  </div></section><section class="section"><div class="wrap blog-grid"><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/visuals/en-feature-map-1600.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt map showing nearby EV charging stations" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 8 min read</p><h2>EV charging station near me: how to find and verify one</h2><p>Learn how to find nearby EV chargers and check connector, power, access, price and recent conditions before leaving.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/ev-charging-station-near-me">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-economy-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt charging cost and savings screen" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 9 min read</p><h2>How much does it cost to charge an electric car?</h2><p>Calculate an EV charging estimate using battery capacity, energy price, charging losses, parking fees and session charges.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/how-much-does-it-cost-to-charge-an-electric-car">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-point-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="Electric car charging information in VeVolt" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 8 min read</p><h2>How long does it take to charge an electric car?</h2><p>Understand how charger power, vehicle limits, battery level and temperature affect electric-car charging time.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/how-long-does-it-take-to-charge-an-electric-car">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-point-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt screen with charging-station connector details" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 9 min read</p><h2>Electric-car connectors: Type 2, CCS2, CHAdeMO and GB/T</h2><p>Identify common EV charging connectors and verify compatibility before choosing a charging station.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/electric-car-connectors-type-2-ccs2-chademo-gbt">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-route-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt route and estimated battery on arrival" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 10 min read</p><h2>How to plan an electric-car trip with charging stops</h2><p>Plan an EV road trip using range, compatible chargers, alternatives, charging time and safe arrival margins.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/how-to-plan-an-electric-car-trip">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-condo-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt Condo shared charging management screen" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 11 min read</p><h2>Electric-car charging in a condominium: what to organize</h2><p>Understand electrical assessment, approval, safety, scheduling, consumption records and cost allocation for shared EV charging.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/electric-car-charger-in-condominium">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-route-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="Fast-charging location details shown in VeVolt" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 8 min read</p><h2>Fast charging an electric car: practical best practices</h2><p>Use DC fast charging efficiently by checking compatibility, battery level, charging curve, queue and stop duration.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/fast-charging-electric-car-best-practices">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-point-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt charging location with tariff information" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 7 min read</p><h2>Free or paid EV charging station: how to know before arriving</h2><p>Check electricity price, parking charges, session fees, access rules and operator requirements before using an EV charger.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/free-or-paid-ev-charging-station">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-community-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt Community reports for an EV charging station" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 8 min read</p><h2>How to check whether an EV charger is working</h2><p>Reduce uncertainty by checking operator status, recent driver reports, access conditions and nearby alternatives.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/how-to-check-if-an-ev-charger-is-working">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/visuals/en-feature-market-1600.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt map and nearby charging services" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 10 min read</p><h2>Can you own an electric car without a home charger?</h2><p>Assess public charging, workplace access, routine distance, charging time and cost before relying on an EV without home charging.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/electric-car-without-home-charger">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/visuals/en-feature-premium-1600.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt economy dashboard comparing electric charging costs" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 9 min read</p><h2>Electric car versus gasoline: how to compare cost per kilometer</h2><p>Compare electricity and fuel fairly using real consumption, energy price, charging losses and the same distance period.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/electric-car-versus-gasoline-cost-per-kilometer">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/visuals/en-feature-map-1600.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt map of charging stations in Brazil" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 8 min read</p><h2>EV charging-station map in Brazil: how to read the network in 2026</h2><p>Understand public and semi-public charging coverage, connector data, regional gaps and what a map marker really means.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/ev-charging-station-map-brazil-2026">Read article →</a></div></article><article class="article-card"><img src="/assets/screens/en-market-720.webp" width="720" height="405" alt="VeVolt Market showing nearby businesses and EV services" loading="lazy"><div class="article-card-body"><p class="article-meta">Updated 18/07/2026 · 7 min read</p><h2>EV charging at shopping centers, supermarkets and hotels</h2><p>Check access, parking, session activation, stay limits and etiquette when charging at a destination.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/blog/how-to-use-ev-charging-at-shopping-centers-hotels">Read article →</a></div></article></div></section><section class="cta-band"><div class="wrap cta-inner"><div><h2>Find the energy to keep moving.</h2><p>Find charging stations, check community updates, plan your route and track electric mobility costs in one app.</p></div><div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href="/en/testers">Join the test</a><a class="button secondary" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=br.com.vevolt" rel="noopener">Open Google Play</a></div></div></section></main>
